          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἄλγος</span></b> : <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">pain;</span>
          freq. met., and esp. pl., <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">hardship, troubles, woe;</span> of
          hunters, <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">οἵ τε καθ᾽ ὕ̄λην</span> | <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἄλγεα πάσχουσιν</span>, <i><span class="en">Od.
